channel.title: New rs 07 videos
channel.description:
RS07 User: Kr0nic Rng Channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/k1dkr0nic
I made a new youtube channel when rs07 was released. I already have a few videos up to be watched, and a lot more to come. Let me know what type of videos you think would make my channel/videos better (preferably only if you already watched alteast a few of what I got) I plan on showing more pking at the end of my progress videos for now on, just like my new path of a pker series shows, and complete pk montages and commentaries once my account if finished or closer to hitting my goals. I have been told and do understand I need to work on my commentary so please don't spam that but I do plan on working on that as much as just getting up my stats and making more entertaining content.
If you like what you see, or just want to give it a chance for a while to see if it improves I will really appreciate some subscriptions, likes, and comments on my videos, -Thanks for reading all this and giving the channel a chance (if you do lol) I hope you enjoy, sub, and continue watching future videos..
I wasn't sure if I could advertise my channel in this section tbh but since it is a rs07 channel with a lot of rs07 progress vids, bank vids, and pking, I didn't see why it would be a problems. (plus I couldn't find a rules thread in this section.) If this thread needs to be moved or something though then ight (:
RS07 User: Kr0nic Rng Channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/k1dkr0nic
